snippet.title: Zenless Zone Zero State of Play Announcement Video
snippet.description:
PlayStation®5 version in development!

Dear citizens, the route to New Eridu is currently closed for construction.
We apologize for the inconvenience. Thank you for your support and understanding.
We look forward to seeing you in New Eridu!

Follow the official Zenless Zone Zero community for more prizes and events:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ZZZ_EN
Discord: https://discord.gg/zenlesszonezero
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/ZZZ_Official/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ZZZ.Official.EN
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@zenlesszonezero

#zzzero #ZZZ
